snippet.title: Celebrity Martini
snippet.description:
A channel dedicated to celebs.

The goal is simply to entertain, have a little bit of fun, & hopefully a few laughs.
Subscribe for daily videos. 

Please note that my channel is not monetized nor do I make money from it, it's just for fun and to entertain, therefore if you'd like to buy me a little cup of coffee I'd really appreciate it!

☕  https://www.buymeacoffee.com/jmartini

Also, note that I do not own some of these videos therefore for any questions or issues please do not hesitate to contact me.

Thank you for your support :)
